===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# A great [[attention]] and concern from someone or something.
# The price paid for obtaining, or price received for providing, [[money]] or [[goods]] in a [[credit]] [[transaction]], calculated as a fraction of the amount or value of what was [[borrow]]ed.
# Attention that is given to or received from someone or something.
# A [[business]] or [[amorous]] [[link]] or [[involvement]].
#: ''I have business '''interests''' in South Africa.''

